# Code of Conduct

# Purpose

This repository promotes respectful collaboration and educational research.

---

# Expected Behavior

Participants should:

- Be respectful
- Use professional language
- Support learning
- Share constructive feedback

---

# Unacceptable Behavior

The following are prohibited:

- Harassment
- Hate speech
- Threats
- Illegal content
- Malicious activity

---

# Cybersecurity Ethics

All discussions and contributions must remain:

- legal
- educational
- research-focused

This repository does not support illegal activities.

---

# Reporting Problems

Users may report inappropriate behavior through GitHub Issues or repository contact methods.

---

# Enforcement

Maintainers may remove content violating repository standards.
